{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"935047b413","title":"中央对华北局一份情况通报的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8ecaa96a2e","index":0,"year":1952,"month":4,"day":8,"articleId":"935047b413","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"248bdf0620","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"935047b413","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央华北局1952年4月5日关于华北区十二个省属市工商联和同业公会改造问题给各省、市委并报中央的情况通报。"},{"id":"a404713e61","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"935047b413","publication":{},"article":{},"index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这段话加括号写在上述情况通报中关于改造工商联和同业公会的以下一段话之后：“应在运动中本着能充分代表各行业及大、中、小户利益的组织原则，有计划有步骤地进行改造工作，在改选时应特别注意到吸收五反中比较好的大资本家参加。"}],"contents":[{"id":"65c08facce","type":"title","text":"中央对华北局一份情况通报的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"935047b413","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"248bdf0620","type":"paragraph","text":"此件则发给各中央局、分局并转省市区党委参考。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"935047b413","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a404713e61","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"935047b413","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4079acf4e7","type":"paragraph","text":"四月八日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"935047b413","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5a253f3cb5","type":"paragraph","text":"工商联委员的成分，在大城市应以大资本家为主，这和中小城市是不同的。因为中小城市大资本家很少，中小资本家很多，故大资本家所占委员数目不能太多，但亦应尽可能吸收一批大的参加。——中央注